    "content": "<h2>Délka</h2>\n<p><strong>Délka</strong> je fyzikální veličina, která vyjadřuje vzdálenost mezi dvěma body. Značíme ji <strong>l</strong> (nebo s, d, h).</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 460 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <rect x='30' y='35' width='400' height='30' rx='3' fill='#fef3c7' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <line x1='30' y1='35' x2='30' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='1.5'/><text x='30' y='80' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>0</text><line x1='50' y1='42' x2='50' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='70' y1='42' x2='70' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='90' y1='42' x2='90' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='110' y1='42' x2='110' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='130' y1='35' x2='130' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='1.5'/><text x='130' y='80' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>5</text><line x1='150' y1='42' x2='150' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='170' y1='42' x2='170' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='190' y1='42' x2='190' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='210' y1='42' x2='210' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='230' y1='35' x2='230' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='1.5'/><text x='230' y='80' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>10</text><line x1='250' y1='42' x2='250' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='270' y1='42' x2='270' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='290' y1='42' x2='290' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='310' y1='42' x2='310' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='330' y1='35' x2='330' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='1.5'/><text x='330' y='80' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>15</text><line x1='350' y1='42' x2='350' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='370' y1='42' x2='370' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='390' y1='42' x2='390' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='410' y1='42' x2='410' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='0.8'/><line x1='430' y1='35' x2='430' y2='65' stroke='#92400e' stroke-width='1.5'/><text x='430' y='80' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>20</text>\n  <text x='460' y='55' fill='#374151' font-size='11'>cm</text>\n  <line x1='70' y1='22' x2='270' y2='22' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <polygon points='70,18 70,26 62,22' fill='#ef4444'/><polygon points='270,18 270,26 278,22' fill='#ef4444'/>\n  <text x='170' y='17' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='12' font-weight='bold'>l = 10 cm = 0,1 m</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Jednotky délky</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Jednotka</th><th>Značka</th><th>Převod</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>kilometr</td><td>km</td><td>1 km = 1 000 m</td></tr>\n<tr><td>metr</td><td>m</td><td>základní jednotka</td></tr>\n<tr><td>decimetr</td><td>dm</td><td>1 dm = 0,1 m</td></tr>\n<tr><td>centimetr</td><td>cm</td><td>1 cm = 0,01 m</td></tr>\n<tr><td>milimetr</td><td>mm</td><td>1 mm = 0,001 m</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Měřidla délky</h3>\n<p><strong>Pravítko</strong>, metr skládací, krejčovský metr, posuvné měřítko, pásmo, laserový dálkoměr.</p>\n<h3>Postup při měření</h3>\n<p>1. Zvol vhodné měřidlo. 2. Přilož měřidlo správně (počátek stupnice). 3. Odečti hodnotu kolmo ke stupnici. 4. Zapiš výsledek s jednotkou.</p>"
  }
}
